OL,3,CActor Nigel Havers takes on new role
OL,4,Cas pothole campaigner
OL,6,FNigel Havers is the latest celebrity
OL,7,Fto take up the fight against poor road
OL,8,Fconditions. He speaks to ITV News
OL,9,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,11,FTV and film star Nigel Havers, whose
OL,12,Fappearances include Chariots of Fire
OL,13,Fand Coronation Street, has taken on a
OL,14,Fnew role - as a prominent pothole
OL,15,Fcampaigner.
OL,17,FThe car loving celebrity says his own
OL,18,Fvehicle suffered bad pothole damage
OL,19,Fand he's now convinced motorists are
OL,20,Fgetting a raw deal.
