OL,3,CActor Nigel Havers takes on new role
OL,4,Cas pothole campaigner
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, he said: "I am
OL,7,Findeed a pothole campaigner - and like
OL,8,Feverybody else I've had enough of
OL,9,Fthese craters.
OL,11,F"To give a bit of advice for the
OL,12,Fpeople in government, if you leave a
OL,13,Fpothole too long it's gonna cost you
OL,14,Ftwice as much to mend it... so mend it
OL,15,Fstraight away. It'll save you money in
OL,16,Fthe long run."
OL,18,FNigel Havers joins a galaxy of
OL,19,Fcelebrities who have taken up the
OL,20,Ffight against poor road conditions.
