OL,3,CActor Nigel Havers takes on new role
OL,4,Cas pothole campaigner
OL,6,FMusic star Sir Rod Stewart, film icon
OL,7,FArnold Schwarzenegger, broadcaster
OL,8,FJeremy Clarkson and dancer Louie
OL,9,FSpence have all used their status to
OL,10,Fhighlight the problem of Britain's
OL,11,Fbroken roads.
OL,13,FLatest figures from the RAC show the
OL,14,Faverage cost of pothole damage to a
OL,15,Fvehicle is now #460.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the AA reports 1,700 cars
OL,18,Fneeding repairs each day - and an
OL,19,Foverall annual cost of #597m.
