OL,3,CActor Nigel Havers takes on new role
OL,4,Cas pothole campaigner
OL,6,FHavers said: "Why don't they mend them
OL,7,Fthat's all I'm asking, where is the
OL,8,Fmoney going?
OL,10,F"You pay so much for a road tax - a
OL,11,Fhuge amount - and where does that
OL,12,Fmoney go? It doesn't go into mending
OL,13,Fpotholes!"
OL,15,FITV News spoke to Alan Piggott who
OL,16,Fowns a garage in Cambridgeshire which
OL,17,Frepairs almost 2,000 alloy wheels a
OL,18,Fyear due to pothole damage.
